<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> als wir ewch vormals
              <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von geleits <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir
                <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Steinberg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, bey ewch ze <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan> hett, darauf etlich ewr frewnde
              <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> rats <expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> bey uns
                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie ir meint, daz unser <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
            geleits bey ewch niht <expan>notdurft<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> etc., also <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                <expan>fr<ex>ewntschaft</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fleiszikl<ex>ich,</ex></expan> daz ir dem <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> zu ewch, bey ewch und von ewch ewr slecht geleyt
                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wellet, wenn er des an ewch begere, daz er sein
            notdurft bey ewch gehandeln und <expan>ausgetrag<ex>en</ex></expan> mug, <add>wan auch
              er uns sagt, daz im des ein notdurft sey</add>, und ewch gen
              <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Steinberg<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> also frewntlich beweiset, als wir den
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey uns auch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun. Das
                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir etc. Und lat uns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
            ewr <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dem <expan>bott<ex>en.</ex></expan><expan>
                Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.
          </ab>
</div>
